            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"09-monte-carlo-expected-loss\">09 -- Monte Carlo Expected Loss</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Instead of averaging PGA across 500 sources before applying HAZUS (wrong -- nonlinear),\napply HAZUS to each of the 500 scenarios separately, then average the losses.\nWeight = 1/500 (uniform -- UCERF3 noted as future improvement).</span></span>"
